{"tid":619440,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"apple服務真係好好","createTime":"2018-04-06T15:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T18:19:49.000Z","uid":34764,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfddb974a2a2cdb5ee9c91b28eb63cacacbe0cec","tid":619440,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"近排成日打開部macbook，個login畫面就freeze左郁唔到又打唔到字，要熄左再開過先得， 好煩 <br />\n今朝重新開幾十次都係咁 ，死死氣拎去整 ，心諗唔知要整幾多日， 仲要做project架嘛真黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好早去到walk in genius bar， 原本睇完張單都淨係話換trackpad條cable<br />\n11點擺低部機 ，4點已經打黎話整好拎得 ，拎返部機返去再睇返個email先發覺佢幫我換哂成個top case舊電keyboard喇叭全部都係新啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我部機原本勁多撞崩左既位，左邊個喇叭又勁拆聲(要較哂d聲音去右聲道先得），舊電比起之前去得勁快，一分鐘跌1%咁，但呢d野我都無同藍精靈講過，我原本淨係想快d整好比我用得返部機就得<br />\n佢地竟然自動幫我換哂，而家聽野左聲道完全無拆聲，舊電正常返，機身光滑無崩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係2015版macbook pro，有買apple care，仲有4個月就到期，如果有得繼續買第4年就好，部機想一直用落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以後會鍚住部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> apple服務真係好好， 真係值得比錢佢地賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a85db065db515e5fb0d71f98fda4ab50cce44bd","tid":619440,"uid":106506,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"Hardware就<br />\nSoftware就問題推嚟推去"},{"pid":"9b9154dec4bedd4d8af3ad4e4c1dd9345b22bd63","tid":619440,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"2014 年HP機 冇壞過 覆緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14bdcdf53d5f2ddcc0c76c0c8a98ba96503dd6","tid":619440,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9154dec4bedd4d8af3ad4e4c1dd9345b22bd63","tid":619440,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"2014 年HP機 冇壞過 覆緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"2012 acer機覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02ce246dd44edfd3bd61b1756392fc178c350e9","tid":619440,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae14bdcdf53d5f2ddcc0c76c0c8a98ba96503dd6","tid":619440,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9154dec4bedd4d8af3ad4e4c1dd9345b22bd63","tid":619440,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"2014 年HP機 冇壞過 覆緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"2012 acer機覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"2001年 Tiny 機覆你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}